TITLE: ContextLoggerModule Integration with Pino (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how nestjs-context-logger integrates with Pino using nestjs-pino under the hood. It demonstrates how to configure the ContextLoggerModule with regular Pino options such as log level and transport. This integration preserves all Pino formatting and transport options while adding context management through AsyncLocalStorage.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adird/nestjs-context-logger/blob/main/README.md#_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
@Module({
  imports: [
    ContextLoggerModule.forRoot({
      // Regular Pino options
      pinoHttp: {
        level: 'info',
        transport: {
          target: 'pino-pretty'
        }
      }
    })
  ]
})
```

