TITLE: Context Logger Example (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates logging with context enrichment using nestjs-context-logger in TypeScript. This example shows an error message logged with additional context information like correlationId, userId, subscriptionTier, etc.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adird/nestjs-context-logger/blob/main/README.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// With nestjs-context-logger ðŸŽ‰
