TITLE: AsyncLocalStorage Context Cleanup (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This demonstrates how AsyncLocalStorage automatically cleans up context when the execution context exits.  The context is cleaned up at the end of each request, if an error occurs, when all async operations in the chain complete, or even if you forget to clean up manually.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adird/nestjs-context-logger/blob/main/README.md#_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// When this completes, context is eligible for garbage collection
ContextLogger.runWithCtx(async () => {
  await handleRequest();
  // After this, context is cleaned up
});
```

