TITLE: AsyncLocalStorage Context Isolation in nestjs-context-logger (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how nestjs-context-logger creates its own AsyncLocalStorage instance.  This instance is automatically isolated from other ALS instances in the application code, other libraries, and other parts of the system.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adird/nestjs-context-logger/blob/main/README.md#_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// Inside nestjs-context-logger package
const globalStore = new AsyncLocalStorage<Record<string, any>>();
```

