TITLE: Log Field Grouping Configuration (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Configuration for grouping log fields under specific keys (bindingsKey, contextKey). This example shows how to organize log fields into 'metadata' and 'params' for better queryability.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adird/nestjs-context-logger/blob/main/README.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
ContextLoggerModule.forRoot({
  groupFields: {
    bindingsKey: 'params',    // Groups runtime bindings
    contextKey: 'metadata'    // Groups context information
  }
})
```

