DESCRIPTION: These commands clone the repository, install dependencies, and run tests to verify the initial setup. It ensures the development environment is properly configured before making changes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adird/nestjs-context-logger/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md#_snippet_0

