TITLE: Importing ContextLoggerModule in AppModule
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code snippet imports and includes the `ContextLoggerModule` in the `AppModule` of a NestJS application. This makes the context-aware logger available for use within the application.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adird/nestjs-context-logger/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { ContextLoggerModule } from 'nestjs-context-logger';

@Module({
  imports: [ContextLoggerModule],
})
export class AppModule {}
```

